harnessRequest.name: CPM Shared Process Test #3
harnessRequest.description: Can we use a cell that uses a proxy as a helper? NO! WE CANNOT DO THIS YET. THIS IS PLANNED FOR v0.0.49.

constructorRequest.name: CPM Shared Process Test #3
constructorRequest.description: Can we use a cell that uses a proxy as a helper?

cellmodel.name: CPP Test Model 3
cellmodel.description: Embeds CPP Test Model 2 as a helper cell to test if the CPM memory manager can correctly handle the helper cell's requests when it's functioning as a helper.

7dTIJgcz6Kix1JUYAtzV2g.name: CPP Test Model 3
7dTIJgcz6Kix1JUYAtzV2g.description: Embeds CPP Test Model 2 as a helper cell to test if the CPM memory manager can correctly handle the helper cell's requests when it's functioning as a helper.

XP3yxl1ciE5MsHkhdn5iQQ.name: CPP Test Process 3
XP3yxl1ciE5MsHkhdn5iQQ.description: Declares that this cell uses and owns a copy of CPP Test Model 2 whose lifespan is tied to this cell's lifespan (whatever role it's functioning in).

7dTIsQcz6Jax1JUjAtzVNw.name: CPP Test Model 2
7dTIsQcz6Jax1JUjAtzVNw.description: A model that embeds a proxy. We use this model to ensure that a cell cannot tell if its role is helper (i.e. embedded in another model's ocdDataSpec via an object namesspace APM binding annotaton).

XP3yGl1ciCtMsHnMdn5i3A.name: CPP Test Model 2
XP3yGl1ciCtMsHnMdn5i3A.description: A process that tests a cell's ability to use a cell proxy equivalent regardless of it itself is a helper cell (owned by a cell process). Or, a cell process (either owned or shared).

z87s3cCZJi2mPmXJ8r37qA.name: Messenger Model
z87s3cCZJi2mPmXJ8r37qA.description: A simple cell model to transport a something between cells.

blVAl6l4wc87xvb0Bgdidg.name: Messenger Process
blVAl6l4wc87xvb0Bgdidg.description: A simple cell process declaration that models an untyped containter cell intended to be used for testing generic message passing protocols using the CPM as the means of delivery.

7dTIIAcz6BCx1JV5AtzVSw.name: CPP Test 2A
7dTIIAcz6BCx1JV5AtzVSw.description: A model that attempts to create a child process. We use this model to ensure that a cell cannot tell if its role is helper. Or, is active as a cell process (either owned or shared).

XP3y711ciGxMsHkhdn5i0w.name: CPP Test 2A
XP3y711ciGxMsHkhdn5i0w.description: A process that attempts to create a child process. We use this model to ensure that a cell cannot tell if its role is helper. Or, is active as a cell process (either owned or shared).

7dTI7Qcz6HCx1JWZAtzVjw.name: CPP Test Model 2B
7dTI7Qcz6HCx1JWZAtzVjw.description: A model that embeds helpers at various depths of its process memory space to test CPM's ability to track cell ownership correctly.

XP3y-l1ciDBMsHnzdn5iWg.name: CPP Test Process 2B
XP3y-l1ciDBMsHnzdn5iWg.description: A process that embeds owned helper processes at various depths of its process memory space to test CPM's ability to track cell ownership correctly.

7dTIOQcz6LOx1JWmAtzVJg.name: CPP Test Model 2C
7dTIOQcz6LOx1JWmAtzVJg.description: A model that embeds our other experiments to test yet more combinations of various cell and helper cell interconnect topologies.

XP3ymV1ciAdMsHnBdn5ilw.name: CPP Test Process 2C
XP3ymV1ciAdMsHnBdn5ilw.description: A process that embeds our other experiments to test yet more combinations of various cell and helper cell interconnect topologies.

FvUW9UtwS3DDHsMeWSJZIg.description: Cell process manager root process for CellProcessor CPM Shared Process Test #3 Runtime Host.

ZtVm1b_mv-b3Mvcy7KzsrA.description: Cell process manager root process for CellProcessor CPM Shared Process Test #3 Runtime Host.

DxL0zD_ERu-0kNGX2FvoGg.name: Cell Process Manager: Operator Request On Cell (opOn)
DxL0zD_ERu-0kNGX2FvoGg.description: Generically re-routes the TransitionOperator request specified by operatorRequest to the active cell indicated by apmBindingPath + path, or path (iff path is fully-qualified).

9tNY7o5GTUGH_xda2GhP-w.name: Cell Process Manager: Cell In Step Operator
9tNY7o5GTUGH_xda2GhP-w.description: Returns Boolean true iff the indicated cell is active and is in one of N >=1 APM process step label(s).

gJnA-VJTTLa0g9TKFmjv1Q.name: Cell Process Manager: Ancestor Processes Active
gJnA-VJTTLa0g9TKFmjv1Q.description: Return Boolean true if request.context.apmBindingPath is a cell process with active ancestor processes.

6j5F3HmKTLG9Q8kD1-QWYA.name: Cell Process Manager: Ancestor Processes All In Step
6j5F3HmKTLG9Q8kD1-QWYA.description: Returns Boolean true if request.context.apmBindingPath is a cell process with ancestor process(es) all in the specified process step(s).

jFxFmpHSSPaeWEFfLh8eWw.name: Cell Process Manager: Ancestor Processes Any In Step
jFxFmpHSSPaeWEFfLh8eWw.description: Returns Boolean true if request.context.apmBindingPath is a cell process with ancestor process(es) any of which are in the specified process step(s).

xIRhBHueTRGO0xq63UUbyQ.name: Cell Process Manager: Child Processes Active
xIRhBHueTRGO0xq63UUbyQ.description: Returns Boolean true iff request.context.apmBindingPath is a cell process with one or more child cell processes.

5P2MHjL4TXCqScp_xNrJyA.name: Cell Process Manager: Child Processes All In Step
5P2MHjL4TXCqScp_xNrJyA.description: Returns Boolean true request.context.apmBindingPath is a cell process whose child processes are all in the specified process step.

esuJGgmERrSV3AFvFOMyhw.name: Cell Process Manager: Child Processes Any In Step
esuJGgmERrSV3AFvFOMyhw.description: Returns Boolean true request.context.apmBindingPath is a cell process with any child cell process in the specified process step.

Fs6tE76WR5yTOdbwQ_N_FQ.name: Cell Process Manager: Descendant Processes Active
Fs6tE76WR5yTOdbwQ_N_FQ.description: Returns Boolean true if request.context.apmBindingPath is a cell process with active dependant cell processes.

DX5GfJcwRNq0xW20KzMSJQ.name: Cell Process Manager: Descendant Processes All In Step
DX5GfJcwRNq0xW20KzMSJQ.description: Returns Boolean true request.context.apmBindingPath is a cell process with all descendant cell processes in the specified process step.

DzlsRZBOReO03GSPsU3CIg.name: Cell Process Manager: Descendant Processes Any In Step
DzlsRZBOReO03GSPsU3CIg.description: Returns Boolean true request.context.apmBindingPath is a cell process whose descendant cell processes contain any cell process(es) in the specified process step.

9HNGDusyTtKpleXFae7O5A.name: Cell Process Manager: Parent Process Active
9HNGDusyTtKpleXFae7O5A.description: Returns Boolean true iff request.context.apmBindingPath is a cell process with an active parent process.

PHPSWivjRyK80Gtymsp-pA.name: Cell Process Manager: Parent Process In Step
PHPSWivjRyK80Gtymsp-pA.description: Returns Boolean true request.context.apmBindingPath is a cell process whose parent cell process is in the specified process step.

VNaA0AMsTXawb32xLaNGTA.name: Cell Process Manager: Initialize
VNaA0AMsTXawb32xLaNGTA.description: Performs initialization of Cell Process Manager cell process (the root and parent process of all cell processes executing in a CellProcess runtime host instance).

SdL0-5kmTuiNrWNu7zGZhg.name: Cell Process Manager: Process Create
SdL0-5kmTuiNrWNu7zGZhg.description: Create a new child cell process bound to the specified APM that is owned by the requesting cell process, #. Or, the specified parent cell process (via override).

4s_DUfKnQ4aS-xRjewAfUQ.name: Cell Process Manager: Process Delete
4s_DUfKnQ4aS-xRjewAfUQ.description: Requests that the Cell Process Manager delete a branch of the cell process tree.

r-JgxABoS_a-mSE2c1nvKA.name: Cell Process Manager: Process Query
r-JgxABoS_a-mSE2c1nvKA.description: Performs a query on a specific cell process managed by the Cell Process Manager.

wB5QKMYtS7yY2-v7Y3tGWA.name: Cell Process Manager: ControllerAction Request On Cell (actOn)
wB5QKMYtS7yY2-v7Y3tGWA.description: Generically re-routes the ControllerAction request specified by actRequest to the active cell specified by apmBindingPath + path, or path (iff path is fully-qualified).

LG9CCSEmSYaU6Mp9J0wZ5g.name: Cell Process Proxy Helper Model
LG9CCSEmSYaU6Mp9J0wZ5g.description: A resuable helper cell model that allows developers to link namespace(s) defined in their own AbstractProcessModel(s) memory specifications to other cell processes.

CPPU-UPgS8eWiMap3Ixovg.name: Holarchy Cell Process Proxy Helper Process
CPPU-UPgS8eWiMap3Ixovg.description: Defines a helper process that functions as a proxy for action and operator calls to some (any) shared cell process.

c-n6U_maQa23j9jWFDsgOw.name: Cell Process Proxy: Proxy Status
c-n6U_maQa23j9jWFDsgOw.description: Returns Boolean true if the cell process proxy helper cell was logically connected to an owned local cell process that has been deleted.

FTxze-WaRp6HS0Dlr_Ke6A.name: Cell Process Proxy: Proxy Operator
FTxze-WaRp6HS0Dlr_Ke6A.description: Forwards the specified operator request to the local cell process to which the proxy is currently connected.

X6ck_Bo4RmWTVHl-vk-urw.name: Cell Process Proxy: Connect Proxy
X6ck_Bo4RmWTVHl-vk-urw.description: Disconnect a connected cell process proxy process (if connected). And, connect the proxy to the specified local cell process.

ySiBEGcaRGWVOZmwBRyhrA.name: Cell Process Proxy: Disconnect Proxy
ySiBEGcaRGWVOZmwBRyhrA.description: Disconnect a connected cell process proxy from whatever local cell process it is currently connected to.

rua1glcmTsOlYcfpZuiXnA.name: Cell Process Proxy: Proxy Action
rua1glcmTsOlYcfpZuiXnA.description: Forwards the specified action request to the local cell process to which the proxy is currently connected.

MDVBKW89TvO9T62Ge7GmNg.name: Holarchy Core
MDVBKW89TvO9T62Ge7GmNg.description: Low-level glue models, actions, and operators for building re-usable infrastructure for execution within an ObservableProcessController (OPC) runtime host instance.

RW8Y2O-kRNSv87yXT962wQ.name: Holarchy Core Logic
RW8Y2O-kRNSv87yXT962wQ.description: A collection of TranitionOperator plug-ins that implement generic logic functions AND, OR, NOT, TRUE.

YgABX95wR86GCYrYaDLISA.name: Logical AND
YgABX95wR86GCYrYaDLISA.description: Returns Boolean true iff all suboperations return true.

0JIva4IFSm6Xm7i38g8uUA.name: Logical OR
0JIva4IFSm6Xm7i38g8uUA.description: Returns Boolean true iff any suboperations return true.

TLSHkl73SO-utuzM7dyN2g.name: Logical NOT
TLSHkl73SO-utuzM7dyN2g.description: Returns Boolean true iff the suboperator returns false (i.e. it logically complements or inverts whatever operator it's applied to).

e89cwnP4Qd6MocAhzdOJgw.name: Logical TRUE
e89cwnP4Qd6MocAhzdOJgw.description: Always returns Boolean true. Used typically to unilaterally transition a cell process from one step to another (e.g. always, or as a default after many other transition rules).

jQxlhOe-RDilxY0sNIierQ.name: Holarchy Core Memory Actions & Operators
jQxlhOe-RDilxY0sNIierQ.description: A collection of ControllerAction & TransitionOperator plug-ins that perform logical comparisons operatations on cell processs memory.

oaF3-dXwQkusjD3I2o9-8g.name: OCD Array Length Equal to Value
oaF3-dXwQkusjD3I2o9-8g.description: Returns Boolean true iff the length of the array stored at OCD path equals the specified numerical value (direct or indirect).

2w7n6KxdR8mdIliePJesLQ.name: OCD Namespace A ? B Value Comparison
2w7n6KxdR8mdIliePJesLQ.description: Returns Boolean true iff operand A and B values compare using the indicated comparison operator. Note either A and/or B may be specified by value or path.

UeLs9PcASwuC7KR190eYhA.name: OCD Boolean Flag Is Set
UeLs9PcASwuC7KR190eYhA.description: Returns Boolean true iff the indicated Boolean flag namespace is true.

ggsavKiARsq7rjwn-lxdfA.name: OCD Namespace Is Greater Than Value
ggsavKiARsq7rjwn-lxdfA.description: Returns Boolean true iff the indicated OCD namespace is greater than the indicated value. Limited to number and string value comparisons only.

k7THIKKDQMKOac1Rxh9tEQ.name: OCD Namespace Is Identical To Value
k7THIKKDQMKOac1Rxh9tEQ.description: Returns Boolean true iff the indicated OCD namespace is identical (i.e. strictly equal (===)) to the indicated value. Limited to number and string value comparisons only.

XxX_a1sQS1OlJbWAYfx6tQ.name: OCD Namespace Is Less Than Value
XxX_a1sQS1OlJbWAYfx6tQ.description: Returns Boolean true iff the indicated OCD namespace is less than the indicated value. Limited to number and string value comparisons only.

kD1PcgqYQlm7fJatNG2ZsA.name: OCD Namespace Is Truthy
kD1PcgqYQlm7fJatNG2ZsA.description: Returns Boolean true iff the indicated OCD namespace is truthy.

pj9a6tQpSXWp7WZZ8VbKLQ.name: OCD Namespace Is Array Empty
pj9a6tQpSXWp7WZZ8VbKLQ.description: Returns Boolean true iff the indicated OCD namespace value is an array AND value.length !== 0.

fS5liuD1RBSdaPBEhsoxXw.name: OCD Namespace Is Map Keyless
fS5liuD1RBSdaPBEhsoxXw.description: Returns Boolean true iff the indicated OCD namespace is declared as a map in the OCD filter spec AND the OCD value is an object AND Object.key(value) !== 0.

Ve_kEFkGSMSgOqUWu9Yo_w.name: OCD Read Namespace Indirect
Ve_kEFkGSMSgOqUWu9Yo_w.description: Reads and returns the value of OCD namespace via path indirection.

5rFEDGLYRSiZCeChMnkCHQ.name: OCD Boolean Flag Set
5rFEDGLYRSiZCeChMnkCHQ.description: Set the Boolean-type OCD namespace specified by path to value true.

_yxWfFLnTqqN-UxRdd7W5w.name: OCD Boolean Flag Clear
_yxWfFLnTqqN-UxRdd7W5w.description: Set the Boolean-type OCD namespace specified by path to value false.

YtwGXxryRyaNnxwc9NGJiQ.name: Holarchy Core Utility Actions & Operators
YtwGXxryRyaNnxwc9NGJiQ.description: A collection of ControllerAction & TransitionOperator plug-ins that are of general use when building custom APM's in particular.
